         physics, ee_link_offset discovery, strike axis, rewards and hammer
         blows all derive from it. Do NOT re-apply the mole_media 7c95ea6
         (2026-07-03) lidar EE recalibration (2.07 -0.23 0.10 | yaw -0.12) —
